g.text: Cc gi tr ca multiplicity bao gm:
Multiplicity = 1: Mt i tng trong lp A c th lin kt vi mt
i tng trong lp B v ngc li. y l mt quan h mt-mt
Multiplicity = 0..1: Mt i tng trong lp A c th lin kt vi ti
a mt i tng trong lp B v ngc li. y l mt quan h
Multiplicity = 0..* hoc Multiplicity = *: Mt i tng trong lp A c
th lin kt vi mt hoc nhiu i tng trong lp B v ngc li.
y l mt quan h nhiu-nhiu (many-to-many).
Multiplicity = 1..* hoc Multiplicity = +: Mt i tng trong lp A
phi lin kt vi t nht mt i tng trong lp B v c th lin kt
vi nhiu hn. y l mt quan h mt-nhiu (one-to-many).
